.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/z_archive/wave-2-merges/004-runtime-executor-hardening/changelog/changelog-001-foundational-runtime.md:33:- `mcp_server/lib/context/caller-context.ts` exports `runWithCallerContext`, `getCallerContext`, `requireCallerContext`. Transport wraps each request dispatch in `context-server.ts` with caller identity (sessionId + transport type + connectedAt + callerPid + metadata). 12 tests cover propagation across `await`, `setTimeout`, `Promise.all`, nested runs, readonly immutability.
.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/z_archive/wave-2-merges/004-runtime-executor-hardening/changelog/changelog-001-foundational-runtime.md:52:- `handlers/session-resume.ts` binds `args.sessionId` to the caller's MCP-transport-layer session identity via AsyncLocalStorage caller context. `MCP_SESSION_RESUME_AUTH_MODE=permissive` env flag for canary rollout. Default is strict (reject mismatch).
.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/z_archive/wave-2-merges/004-runtime-executor-hardening/changelog/changelog-001-foundational-runtime.md:97:| `mcp_server/handlers/session-resume.ts` | Binds `args.sessionId` to caller-context identity. `MCP_SESSION_RESUME_AUTH_MODE` env flag. |
