.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/z_archive/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/001-hybrid-rag-fusion-epic/research/iterations/iteration-010.md:42:11. **The cognitive subsystem introduces significant parameter complexity into the MCP tool layer.** The `memory_search` tool accepts session-aware parameters (sessionId, enableSessionBoost, enableDedup, enableCausalBoost) that directly trigger cognitive module behavior. The `memory_match_triggers` tool has (include_cognitive, session_id, turnNumber) -- 3 cognitive-specific parameters. Developers must understand session lifecycle, attention decay semantics, and rollout policy to use these effectively. This is a UX friction point for Q3 investigation.
