.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/z_archive/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/001-hybrid-rag-fusion-epic/research/iterations/iteration-011.md:32:6. **Inconsistent casing in TriggerArgs**: Uses `session_id` and `include_cognitive` (snake_case) while ALL other arg interfaces use camelCase (`sessionId`, `includeContent`). This is the ONLY interface with snake_case parameters.
