.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/z_archive/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/001-hybrid-rag-fusion-epic/research/iterations/iteration-017.md:145:TriggerArgs uses `session_id` and `include_cognitive` (snake_case) while all other MCP tool parameter interfaces use camelCase. The same tool (`memory_search`) has duplicate parameters: `minQualityScore` (camelCase) and `min_quality_score` (snake_case) for the same value.
